title: Nature vs. Culture vs. Nutrition
description: 12 action-packed minutes: commenting on a simple point concerning nutritional deficiencies (on a "natural" diet) I then dig into the deeper question of the arbitrary and imperfect relationship between (i) nature, (ii) culture and (iii) nutrition.
